---
source: src/core/procedure.rs
command: ee --workspace <empty-workspace> --json procedure list --limit 3 --include-steps
assertion: procedure list reads persisted procedure records and emits a stable empty-list contract when no records exist
schema:
  list: ee.procedure.list_report.v1
contracts:
  - procedure list is read-only and does not mutate procedure state
  - empty workspaces return procedures as an empty array
  - total_count and filtered_count are explicit numeric fields
  - status filtering preserves deterministic ordering by created_at and procedure_id
  - include-steps does not invent steps when no persisted procedure records exist
  - JSON stdout contains only the machine response
evidence:
  - schema
  - procedures
  - total_count
  - filtered_count
  - procedure_id
  - title
  - status
  - step_count
  - created_at
observed_stdout:
  schema: ee.procedure.list_report.v1
  procedures: []
  total_count: 0
  filtered_count: 0
